<div class="container mb-5">
  <div class="row justify-content-center text-center">
    <div class="h3 text-center my-5">How to navigate Music Tabs?</div>
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-8">
      <div class="accordion" id="accordionNavigate">
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseNavigateOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseNavigateOne">
              <strong class="d-block w-100 text-center">View All Tabs</strong>
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapseNavigateOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#accordionNavigate">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              The list view shows all tabs with titles. Users can click on a tab to view or edit it. A plus (+) button allows adding new tabs.<br>
              <img src="<%= asset_path 'viewTabs.gif' %>" alt="Index view gif" class="big-image img-fluid">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseNavigateTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseNavigateTwo">
              <strong class="d-block w-100 text-center">Create a Tab</strong>
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapseNavigateTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionNavigate">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              Users can create a new tab by entering a title and content. The content field supports rich text formatting and file attachments. Click "Create" to save.
              <img src="<%= asset_path 'createTab.gif' %>" alt="Creating tab gif" class="big-image img-fluid">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseNavigateThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseNavigateThree">
              <strong class="d-block w-100 text-center">View Tab</strong>
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapseNavigateThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionNavigate">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              Users can view the full content of a created tab. The tab displays all the formatted details entered during creation or editing, allowing for easy reference during practice or performance.
              <img src="<%= asset_path 'viewTab.gif' %>" alt="Viewing tab gif" class="big-image img-fluid">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseNavigateFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseNavigateFour">
              <strong class="d-block w-100 text-center">Edit Tab</strong>
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapseNavigateFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionNavigate">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              Users can edit the title and content of an existing tab with rich text options. Save changes after editing.
              <img src="<%= asset_path 'editTab.gif' %>" alt="Editing tab gif" class="big-image img-fluid">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
